  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_schedule_of_growing_skills">Schedule of Growing Skills</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_schedule_of_growing_skills">SGS</xref>
) is a type of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_schedule_of_growing_skills">Schedule of Growing Skills</xref>
 allows 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONALS</xref>
 to establish the developmental levels of children, including areas of strength and potential delay, and covers ages from birth to 5 years.  </p>
  <p>
